John Channell Mills https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Channell_Mills 0 John Channell Mills (26 March 1929 – 16 October 1998) was an English actor, working in the theatre. He was born in London and was the father of comedian Bob Mills and the writer/educationalist Colin Mills.
